{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "戲劇性", "storyInfo": "格蕾塔回應五年前的事故，並軟硬兼施說服劇組實行拍攝天災的計劃；莫伊拉既幫助邁克爾洗清嫌疑，也向蒂比和服裝師瑪麗昂說出了邁克爾想要偷偷逃離地塊一事。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g3_filmset", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_imprisonment_intro", "key": "$m_bat_imprisonment_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士，我們要遭遇天災的消息到底是不是真的？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍卡塢的城際網路覆蓋範圍極廣，即使地塊開出主城區也能接收到天災預警！為什麼我們的終端沒收到提醒？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以最近的通訊訊號時好時壞，難道不是因為我的運氣，而是——", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#4$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊設備被人蓄意破壞！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了！無憑無據的懷疑是沒有任何意義的。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無憑無據？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我偶然在辦公室裡找到一些紙條，拼接之後能看出一份是特里蒙大學發布的天災預測報告，另一份則是分鏡表。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔·斯通女士，上面還有你的親筆簽名，你到底想做什麼？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小子，讓我看看。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是攝影師，我怎麼不知道新增了這幾場戲？", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要在地塊邊緣布置攝影機？那裡沒有任何布景……等等，我明白了。", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔！你*藍卡塢片場術語*故意的？這麼大的事情竟然瞞著我們，你想幹嘛？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿布納，冷靜一點……格蕾塔女士可能只是來不及把最新的拍攝計劃告訴你，謝莉小姐剛剛過世，很多事情還沒交接……", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還幫這個瘋女人說話？她想讓移動地塊無限接近外層風暴拍攝實景天災！我們所有人都有可能死在這裡！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smashtable"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橫眉怒目的攝影師將拍攝設備重重丟在地上。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我受夠了！我現在就要離開這個鬼地方！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是這麼衝動，阿布納。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衝動？瘋了的人是你！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了彌補五年前那部電影票房的巨大虧損，你自己賠了多少資產？後來你的投資屢屢不順，想用這部電影翻身……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，要是這部電影也變成賠錢貨，道爾頓和謝莉的意外是不是會變成你利用的對象？就跟當時那個墜亡的小演員一樣！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼著急，阿布納。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的事情你倒是記得很清楚，但你自己的呢？這是你最近三年以來進入的第幾個劇組？第一個吧？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邋遢、易怒、毫無職業操守。有哪個劇組還會像我一樣把拍攝設備放心地交到你手上？還有哪些活動會僱你當兼職攝影師？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開？當然可以，身為老朋友，我甚至可以同意你不支付違約金。但阿布納，你又能去哪裡呢？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關你什麼事？大不了——", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跳槽？轉行？再也不荼毒任何一顆鏡頭、任何一台攝影設備？你可以說些言過其實的狠話，發惡毒的誓。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你要是真的嫉惡如仇，為什麼還會答應我的邀約，出現在這裡？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還走嗎？能走嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿布納沒有拿起設備，也沒有離開。他被生活和往事扣押在原地，沉默佇立。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於冷靜下來了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往好的地方想想吧。如果這部電影拍攝成功，說不定你能再拿幾個最佳攝影獎。等你片約蜂擁而至的時候，大可拒絕再次加入我的劇組。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說那些夢話，格蕾塔。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從五年前開始就不相信了。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了各位，我知道因為最近的兩起意外，有人想起了我們共同經歷過的往事，有人聽說了一些似是而非的傳聞。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了我們之後的拍攝能團結一心，我正式向諸位作出回應。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在劇組中大部分的人，都是我在五年前的合作對象。當時拍攝現場因設備老舊，發生了一件令人痛心的意外——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位年輕的新人演員勞拉不幸當場身亡。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可以查閱警方的調查結果，一切公開透明，絕無隱情。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍攝天災這個決定與當年的意外唯一有關聯的地方是，我在五年前得到了非常寶貴的一項經驗——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們缺少的從來不是技術，而是膽量。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這不代表我將各位的安危置之度外。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的移動地塊離開藍卡塢主城區前，我拜訪了特里蒙大學的天災預測專家。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從他手中獲得了一份十分精準的分析報告，並將數據輸入地塊導航系統中測試過多次。拍攝地塊會與天災保持安全距離。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊急逃生艙內的陸行艇不會設定使用權限，任何一位劇組工作人員只要覺得生命受到威脅就可以自行使用。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我會成為最後一個離開移動地塊的人。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有問題的話，散會。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，等等。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格、格蕾塔女士……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不會因為把消息抖出來而道歉的！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用緊張，我只想知道你是從誰那裡拿到的文件。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都說了，是我自己——", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跳過說謊的環節。你沒有那個能力，而我沒有那麼多時間。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……關於情報提供者，我有義務保護他們的隱私……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擾亂片場拍攝違反了合約中的第二和第五款條例，你想從金融終端裡看到處罰結果嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但要是有一些特殊的原因也可以對外透露——", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）是盧西恩先生。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿過嘈雜的人群和雜亂的器材，格蕾塔一眼看到了游離於鬧劇之外的那個人。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲林男人坦然接受格蕾塔冷峻的目光，微微頷首，向她致意。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g9_outsidestudio_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，你是說，昨天晚上邁克爾要見的人是你？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但謝莉小姐走後我們不是繼續看電影了嗎？接下來放的是炎國殭屍片……哦——你確實出去了一段時間。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生給我的終端傳了簡訊，他說在攝影棚裡等我，找我諮詢一些非常重要的問題。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起蒂比，那天是我們約好的電影之夜，我不應該中途離開的，別生氣了……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實在生氣……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是在生氣……氣你怎麼不叫我一起。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一邁克爾對你不懷好意，他的花心已經突破了道德底線，或者因為上午拍攝中斷無處發洩，看你好說話就故意欺負你……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，我從來都不會欺負女生的好嗎。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話從你嘴裡說出來沒有半點說服力。有時你對瑪麗昂的態度都很糟糕，更別說其他女生了。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，連涉世未深的小妹妹都能看穿你。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來想叫你陪我的，但邁克爾先生強調只能一個人過去……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也待過幾個劇組了，我很熟悉這種“花招”，以為又是某種欺負人的把戲，不想讓你跟我一起承受。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在藍卡塢工作的時間比你久一點，熟悉的工作類型也更多，再遇到類似的人，你一定要告訴我，我可以幫你想個絕妙的點子報復他們。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……偵探小姐，這些話可以之後再聊嗎？既然小莫伊拉已經幫我作證了，那現在我就沒有嫌疑了吧？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生和謝莉小姐或許真的是偶遇。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們昨天晚上也看到了謝莉小姐離開前的狀態……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心不在焉，魂不守舍，對吧？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。可能她真的已經到極限了……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話是這麼說……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小莫伊拉，你能幫我作證，我真高興。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你的勇敢，畢竟小蒂比對你的保護慾可能比你真正的姐姐還強……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你姐姐還在藍卡塢當演員嗎？要是她跟你一樣可愛……能不能告訴我她的聯絡方式？說不定我還能幫她介紹劇組。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被人當成殺人兇手都沒辦法讓你收斂一下你的濫情嗎？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，我只是隨口問一句而已嘛……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，別轉移話題了。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是沒告訴我，你找莫伊拉的目的是什麼？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想知道。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生，我覺得應該告訴蒂比和瑪麗昂小姐。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉，不要——", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生問我，有什麼方法，可以偷偷離開地塊。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}